{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_53_02",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四月十日　昼",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6667143,
          "startTime": 1.5666667143
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "はー……やっと事務所に戻って来れた～\nロケのせいで眠い、疲れた、お腹空いた～！",
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5466.6666984,
          "startTime": 12.3333333651
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.0666666985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "お、すずじゃん。なんか食べ物持ってない～？\nkana、誕生日なんだよね～。プレゼントも受付中～",
      "startTime": 16.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12899.999999999998,
          "startTime": 29.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5333337467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ギクッ！　ももももももちろん覚えてますわよ！\n夜にはお渡ししますわ。楽しみにしていてくださいまし",
      "startTime": 25.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 31.9166669529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんのお誕生日だから私の漬けた）\n（特別なお漬物とおにぎりを持って来たけど……）",
      "startTime": 36.8163205437,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14417.012789600001,
          "startTime": 51.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "（プレゼントには「SNSでバズるネタが欲しい」って）\n（言ってたの知らなかったわ……漬物はバズらないわよね）",
      "startTime": 45.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 52.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "すずのやつ、絶対kanaの誕生日忘れてたじゃん～\nでも、あんなに怖がって逃げられるとなんか腹立つわ",
      "startTime": 57.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 62.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 68.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12966.666666699994,
          "startTime": 70.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "か、kanaさん。お疲れ様～、そして、お誕生日\nおめでとう！　はい、まずはこれを被って！",
      "startTime": 67.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、勝手に被せんなよ！　髪型崩れるだろ！\nてか何この帽子？　もしかしてこれがプレゼント！？",
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うわよ！　それは事務所に常備してある\nただのパーティーグッズ！　私からのプレゼントは――",
      "startTime": 87.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 92.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "『ネタ見せ100連発！　バズるまで終わりません！\n佐伯遙子フォーエバー！』よ！　ドヤッ！",
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "は……？",
      "startTime": 101.3000104587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ1本目！　ショートコント！\n『開かない自動ドアを変顔で開こうとする遙子』",
      "startTime": 106.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "は！？　ちょ、何何何何！？　怖いんだけど！\n自動ドアに感知されないって存在感薄過ぎだろ！",
      "startTime": 114.1666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ドンドン行くわよ！　2本目、ショートコント！\n『消えたトイレの自動電気を点けようとする遙子』",
      "startTime": 123.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "やめやめ！　こんなショートコント100本も\n見てらんない！　なんか哀愁が凄いし……",
      "startTime": 130.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……kanaさん、喜んでくれると思ったのに……\nうーん……他にバズりそうな持ちネタは……はっ！！",
      "startTime": 140.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "遙子、kanaさんのために心を込めて歌います！\nそれでは聴いて下さい！",
      "startTime": 151.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2299.9999999999827,
          "startTime": 154.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ソロ時代の幻のシングル『キラキラMIR☆CLE』！\n「キラキラ～ミラクル～！　ピカピカハッピーデイ！」",
      "startTime": 159.1206952095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ああああ！　もう静かにして！　そういうのいいから！\n遙子の気持ちは十分伝わったから！",
      "startTime": 168.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "本当に！？　良かったわ～！　あっ、私の動画は自由に\nドンドンSNSに上げて、バズらせてくれていいわよ",
      "startTime": 179.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "上げねーよ！　遙子のギャグを見たい層が\nkanaのSNSをフォローしてる訳ないだろ！",
      "startTime": 187.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "はーあ……大きな声出したらさらにお腹空いた……\n事務所の冷蔵庫になんか食べ物……入ってないかぁ",
      "startTime": 195.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9933.3333333,
          "startTime": 205.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ……kanaさん、良かったらこれ、食べない？\nおにぎりとお漬物。お味噌汁もササっと作れるわよ",
      "startTime": 207.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ！　食べる食べる！　さくらから遙子の漬物は\n美味しいって聞いてたから、気になってたんだよね！",
      "startTime": 218.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_53_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "いっただきまーす！　……うまっ！　美味し過ぎる！\nこれはSNSにも投稿しなくちゃ！　遙子、写真撮って",
      "startTime": 229.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9666.632302500006,
          "startTime": 231.9333333333
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}